snippet.title: Inkulinati - Official Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Inkulinati is an ink-based strategy straight from medieval manuscripts, where a rabbit's bum can be deadlier than a dog's sword. The trailer highlights how you'll be a master of the Living Ink, build your own bestiary, defeat medieval superstars and collect perks to unleash hidden powers.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
